Name: 6ix9ine HD Wallpaper Themes
Description:
6ix9ine HD Wallpaper 4K Backgrounds & Themes for ChromeHere is a great extension with 6ix9ine HD Wallpaper and Background images. 6ix9ine HD wallpaper 4K Backgrounds extension contains images of Tekashi 6ix9ine, American rapper.

This is a great extension for all who love 6ix9ine Tekashi Rapper.
Decorate your Chrome background with high-quality photos provided by Six Nine (6ix9ine). We will update this great extension with new images frequently. 6ix9ine HD Wallpapers, Beautiful Wallpapers and more will make your browsing experience colorful and enjoyable every day!

HOW TO USE:

- Install This extension by clicking on Add to Chrome button and it will be automatically added. Start customizing your browser according to your needs! Please be patient, the first wallpaper loads longest, and the best user experience is what follows.
- On the left side, there is the settings button where you can separately customize all options by adding or removing them from your browser. 6ix9ine 4K Backgrounds & 4k Wallpapers extension gives you the opportunity to have a blank page with only the HD wallpapers, best wallpapers, and backgrounds, or with all these amazing gadgets.
- On the toolbar, we have created a unique option which shows a classic heart-shaped sign which signifies opening a new tab. It does not distract and is almost unnoticeable. HD Wallpapers and best wallpapers and backgrounds will be visible with every new tab!


FEATURES:

-    Local time option
This extension provides you with a local time option wherever you are and it changes as you change your city or country.
-    Local weather option
6ix9ine Wallpaper extension is accurate, so your weather will match with your current destination.
-    Bookmark
Bookmark your favorite websites, stores or whatever with the bookmark option provided by this extension. You can also quickly access to recently seen websites with one click.
-    Games
This extension has many, many games you can play for free while you are browsing.
-    Pick your favs
By clicking at the heart button, you can choose which wallpapers and backgrounds you can use while browsing. If you want one, you can choose that one. You also have the option to reset everything to default.
-    Newsfeed
We provide newsfeed for all the topics related to the theme you have installed. By clicking on the arrow, you can show or hide the feed. Pretty cool right?
-    Quotes and Facts
Be inspired every day, because 6ix9ine Backgrounds & Wallpapers extension provides inspiring quotes and amazing facts every time you open a new tab. 
-    Google or Yahoo!
Choose between Yahoo! and Google search results, and see which are better for you.


This extension covers wallpapers, backgrounds, fanart, wallpaper apps, cool wallpapers, vector wallpapers, 6ix9ine and nicki minaj, 6ix9ine as a kid and more.  Full HD images of 6ix9ine American Rapper will appear with every new tab.

HOW TO UNINSTALL:

How to remove our extension this from Chrome browser:

1) Click on the three horizontal lines icon in the upper right-hand corner of your Chrome browser.
2) Go to “Settings”.
3) In the menu that appears click on “Extensions”.
4) From the list of installed Extensions, find the name of the extension you wish to uninstall.
5) Click on the trash can icon to the right of “Enable” (for the extension you wish to uninstall).
6) Our extension (in this case 6ix9ine HD Wallpapers & Backgrounds extension) should be removed from your Chrome browser.

Disclaimer Note:

This app is made by 6ix9ine fans and the content is not affiliated with, sponsored or approved by any company. If there should be a problem or if we are in breach of copyright, please let us know and we will resolve the issue. Some parts of the extension may contain ads.

You can download extension from our website for free, lovelytab.com, and enjoy exploring more extensions made just for you.

Description:
Heathcliff is a comic strip created by George Gately in 1973 featuring the title character, a wisecracking cat. Now written and…Heathcliff is a comic strip created by George Gately in 1973 featuring the title character, a wisecracking cat. Now written and drawn by Gately's nephew, Peter Gallagher, it is distributed to over 1,000 newspapers by Creators Syndicate, who took over the comic from McNaught Syndicate in 1988. Heathcliff became an animated television series which debuted September 5, 1984. It was the second series based on the Heathcliff comic strip and was produced by DIC Entertainment (titled: Heathcliff & The Cadillac Cats). It ran in syndication until 1988 with a total of 86 episodes. The first show based on the comic strip was Heathcliff and Dingbat, which debuted in 1980 and was produced by Ruby-Spears. Mel Blanc provided the voice of Heathcliff in both series.

This Heathcliff rendition was created by the amazingly talented gyrfalcon65, deviant artist. http://gyrfalcon65.deviantart.com/

Description:
A new tab page for the castle wallpaper. The hottest, most popular HD theme wallpaper page for users. Updated daily.
Castle of Segovia, Spain

Bodingan Castle, England
The castle is an armed building in medieval Europe and the Middle East, and is generally referred to as an armed building as a private residence for lords and nobles, rather than as a fortress for a public defense facility in a town. Due to the different periods and locations of the building, the castle has many different forms and features, but in general there are defensive fortifications such as city walls and cornices.

The castle originally originated in Europe from the 9th to the 10th centuries, when the fall of the Carolingian dynasty led to the division of its territory to different lords and princes. The castle was used by the nobility to control the surrounding land as a base for launching attacks and defending the enemy, so it was also an aggressive and defensive building. In addition to its military use, the castle also exists as a center of administration and a symbol of rights. Castles in towns are often used to control local people and important access routes. Castles in the countryside are often located near natural or architectural facilities that are critical to the life of the surrounding communities, such as mills and fertile land.

!!! DOESN'T WORK IN CHROME 62 AND LATER !!!
I'm planning to fix this, but it might take a while until I get around to do it.


First install this extension, then do the following:
After enabling DevTools Experiments in Chrome (http://islegend.com/development/how-to-enable-devtools-experiments-within-google-chrome/), go to DevTools Settings -> Experiments -> Enable "Allow Custom UI themes". Description:
YouTube dark skin theme : designed specially for night to avoid flash effectYouTube Red Theme since May 25 2017

This extension allows to switch the current YouTube design to a different one with red and brighter colors. At the beginning, it was developed to avoid flash effect during work at night when you want to listen some music.

------

Hi everybody,

I'm the original creator of the "Black and Red Theme for YouTube™", and I created this new one to fit to the latest YouTube Material design even if there is an option for switching to a dark theme.

Once again, I hope it will be used for people like me who find the current theme too clear at night and have a flash effect every time we open a new YouTube window.

----

IMPORTANT : If you don't already have the newest YouTube interface, you have to activate it otherwise you won't be able to make the extension work! To activate the new interface please take a look at there : https://www.youtube.com/new

If it's not working as intended please leave a message.

----

As always I don't collect any data, this is just a theme !

Thank you for any feedback, I'll take a look about your advice.
Please if you encounter an error or a problem, let me know :)

Name: DevTools Theme: Cobalt2 Unofficial
Description:
A highly customized dark theme for Devtools.A customized dark theme for Chrome DevTools based on Wes Bos' Cobalt2.

To enable custom Devtools themes you need to change some settings in Chrome first:

1. Go to chrome://flags/#enable-devtools-experiments and enable Devtools Experiments.
2. Restart chrome. Hint: type chrome://restart in your address bar and hit enter to restart quickly, your tabs will be saved.
3. Open Devtools and go to settings (inside the overflow menu next to the close button).
4. Under the left navigation, click "Experiments".
5. Check the box for "Allow custom UI themes".
6. Close and reopen Devtools, you should now see the Devtools theme you've installed.

Avengers 4 New Tab - Offered by LovelyTab

This is a great extension for all who love amazing Marvel movies with all its cool features.
Decorate your Chrome background with high-quality photos provided by Avengers New Tab HD Theme extension. We will update this great extension with new images frequently. Cool Avengers Infinity War HD Wallpapers, Beautiful Wallpapers and more will make your browsing experience colorful and enjoyable every day!

HOW TO USE:

- Install Avengers 4 New Tab & 4K Backgrounds extension by clicking on Add to Chrome button and it will be automatically added. Start customizing your browser according to your needs! Please be patient, the first wallpaper loads longest, and the best user experience is what follows.
- On the left side, there is the settings button where you can separately customize all options by adding or removing them from your browser. This pics extension gives you the opportunity to have a blank page with only the HD wallpapers, best wallpapers, and backgrounds, or with all these amazing gadgets.
- On the toolbar, we have created a unique option which shows a classic heart-shaped sign which signifies opening a new tab. It does not distract and is almost unnoticeable. HD Wallpapers and best wallpapers and backgrounds will be visible with every new tab!


FEATURES:

-    Local time option
This extension provides you with a local time option wherever you are and it changes as you change your city or country.
-    Local weather option
HD Wallpaper Avengers extension is accurate, so your weather will match with your current destination.
-    Bookmark
Bookmark your favorite websites, stores or whatever with the bookmark option provided by Avengers 4 Theme extension. You can also quickly access to recently seen websites with one click.
-    Games
This beautiful extension has many, many games you can play for free while you are browsing.
-    Pick your favs
By clicking at the heart button, you can choose which wallpapers and backgrounds you can use while browsing. If you want one, you can choose that one. You also have the option to reset everything to default.
-    Newsfeed
We provide newsfeed for all the topics related to the theme you have installed. By clicking on the arrow, you can show or hide the feed. Pretty cool right?
-    Quotes and Facts
Be inspired every day, because Infinity War HD Wallpaper extension provides inspiring quotes and amazing facts every time you open a new tab.

Choose between Yahoo! and Google search results, and see which are better for you.


This extension covers wallpapers, backgrounds, fanart, wallpaper apps, cool wallpapers, vector wallpapers, Avengers 4, Iron Man, Captain America, Thanos photos and more.  Full HD images of this popular Adventure, Sci-Fi movie will appear with every new tab.

HOW TO UNINSTALL:

How to remove our extension from Chrome browser:

1) Click on the three horizontal lines icon in the upper right-hand corner of your Chrome browser.
2) Go to “Settings”.
3) In the menu that appears click on “Extensions”.
4) From the list of installed Extensions, find the name of the extension you wish to uninstall.
5) Click on the trash can icon to the right of “Enable” (for the extension you wish to uninstall).
6) Our extension (in this case Avengers 4 HD Wallpaper & New Tab Theme extension) should be removed from your Chrome browser.

Disclaimer Note:

Name: Northern Lights Themes New Tab
Description:
New themes of Northern Lights is in front of you. If you love nature, this is right extension for you. Northern Lights Themes New Tab will help you enjoy your browsing experience. Except from great images there are many cool features integrated.

Our dedicated team will update this extension with more images regarding Northern Lights Themes New Tab frequently, so you will get the newest Wallpapers and Backgrounds all the time.

Northern Lights Themes New Tab  is simple and easy to use and is appropriate for all ages.

HOW TO INSTALL AND USE:

1. Click add to Chrome and Northern Lights Themes New Tab extension will be installed
2. Carefully chosen images will be randomly presented to you with every New Tab


SIMPLE FEATURES TO ADJUST ACCORDING TO YOUR NEEDS:

-    Local time option
This exetension provides you with a local time option wherever you are
-    Local weather option
Northern Lights Themes New Tab is accurate, so your weather will match with your current destination.
-    Bookmark
Bookmark your favorite websites, stores or whatever with the bookmark option provided by our extension.
-    Show and hide elements
This extension allows you to show and hide all the elements mentioned above.


FEATURES CATEGORY:
Northern Lights Themes New Tab covers all categories regarding this theme – wallpapers, HD Wallpapers, cool wallpapers, vector wallpapers and more.

HOW TO UNINSTALL:

1) Click on the three horizontal lines icon in the upper right-hand corner of your Chrome browser.
2) Go to “Settings”.
3) In the menu that appears click on “Extensions”.
4) From the list of installed Extensions, find the name of the extension you wish to uninstall.
5) Click on the trash can icon to the right of “Enable” (for the extension you wish to uninstall).
6) Our extension (in this case Northern Lights Themes New Tab) should be removed from your Chrome browser.

DISCLAIMER NOTICE:

This extension is made for all nature lovers and the copyright and trademark are owned by their respective owners. If there should be any violations regarding copyright please inform us and we will resolve this issue as soon as possible.

CHECK OUT:

Free-addons is blogging about various subjects and latest news, so make sure you check us out: https//free-addons.com
